variantdescription: with rocket-and-fuel wing-tip pods from the F-89D.
loadnotes: Stations 1 and 8 are fixed wing-tip pods for rockets and fuel. Each can carry 4.5 factors of air-to-air rockets, giving a total of 9 factors with both pods. The pod fuel is included in the internal fuel.
May use AIM-4 IRM and RHMs.
